msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "Our Mission"

msgid "About_Mission_P1"
msgstr "There's a notion that to grow a business, you have to be ruthless. But we know there's a better way to grow. One where what's good for the bottom line is also good for customers."

msgid "About_Mission_P2"
msgstr "We believe businesses can grow with a conscience, and succeed with a soul — and that they can do it with inbound."

msgid "Our Story"
msgstr "Our Story"

msgid "About_Story_P1"
msgstr "As graduate students at MIT in 2004, Brian and Dharmesh noticed a shift in the way people shop and buy."

msgid "About_Story_P2"
msgstr "Consumers were no longer tolerating interruptive bids for their attention — in fact, they had become quite adept at ignoring them."

